Install
=======

Dependencies
------------

- gmake
- pthreads
- libao
- libcurl
- gcrypt[1]
- json-c
- ffmpeg>=3.3 [2]
- UTF-8 console/locale

[1] with blowfish cipher enabled
[2] required: demuxer mov, decoder aac, protocol http and filters volume,
    aformat, aresample

Adding Dependencies for Ubuntu 20.04
------------------------------------

# apt install libavfilter-dev libgcrypt20-dev libcurl4-openssl-dev libao-dev libjson-c-dev

Building Notes
--------------

Edit the Makefile and then type

	make clean && make

You can run the client directly from the source directory now
 
	./pianobar

Or install it by issuing
	
	make install

